daśabhūmīśvaraiḥ, pariśiṣṭabhūmisthitānām agocaratvāt. daśabhūmiprāptair avalokiteśvaramañjuśrīprabhṛtibhir upabhujyamānam iti yāvat. etad uktaṃ bhavati—śuddhāvāsopari ghanavyūhasaṃjñake samyaksaṃbuddhabhuvane yathā bhagavān ānandarūpaḥ sambhogakāyātmā nirmāṇadvāreṇa sakalajagadarthasaṃpādakaḥ śrāvakapratyekabuddhanavabhūmīśvarair apy adṛśyaśarīro daśabhūmīśvarair eva paraṃ bodhisattvair dharmaśravaṇadvāreṇopabhujyamāna āsaṃsāraṃ cakāsti, tathaiva tat sādhyam iti tṛtīyam.

<commentary>saṃpūryetyādi. dānādipāramitā eva guṇā, guṇyante 'bhyasyanta iti kṛtvā. tān saṃpūrya paripūrṇān kṛtvā, yat saṃbuddhānāṃ kṛtyaṃ sakalam avaśyakartavyaṃ kṛtsnaṃ tad api kṛtvā, bhūtakoṭeḥ śūnyatālakṣaṇāyāś cittacaittanirodhātmikāyā yat sākṣāt karaṇaṃ tad api sādhyam astīti pāramitānayasthā evaṃ bruvate caturthaṃ sādhyam iti.</commentary>

idānīṃ mantranayopadiṣṭaṃ saptavidhaṃ sādhyaṃ kathayitum āha—svābhāṅganetyādi. svābhāṅganām āśleṣituṃ śīlaṃ svabhāvo yasya tat svābhāṅganāśleṣi. apetakalpaṃ vyapagatakalpam, kalpanārahitam iti yāvat.
